sourcesContent:
const pizzas = [
  {
    name: "Barbique Chicken",
    varients: ["small", "medium", "large"],
    prices: [{ small: 200, medium: 350, large: 400 }],
    category: "nonveg",
    image: "https://www.dominos.co.in/files/items/Pepper_Barbeque.jpg",
    description: "Delicious barbecue chicken topped with cheese.",
  },
  {
    name: "Non Veg Supreme",
    varients: ["small", "medium", "large"],
    prices: [{ small: 200, medium: 350, large: 400 }],
    category: "nonveg",
    image: "https://www.dominos.co.in/files/items/Non-Veg_Supreme.jpg",
    description:
      "A supreme combination of black olives, onions, grilled mushrooms, pepper BBQ chicken, peri-peri chicken, and grilled chicken rashers.",
  },
  {
    name: "Golden Corn Pizza",
    varients: ["small", "medium", "large"],
    prices: [{ small: 180, medium: 250, large: 360 }],
    category: "veg",
    image: "https://www.dominos.co.in/files/items/Corn_&_Cheese.jpg",
    description:
      "A beautiful blend of corn, tomato sauce, chili flakes, and cheese, offering a delightful taste with every bite.",
  },
  {
    name: "FarmHouse",
    varients: ["small", "medium", "large"],
    prices: [{ small: 200, medium: 300, large: 420 }],
    category: "veg",
    image: "https://www.dominos.co.in/files/items/Farmhouse.jpg",
    description:
      "A delectable combination of jalapeno, paprika, corns, and cheese, offering a crunchy and flavorful experience.",
  },
  {
    name: "Margerita",
    varients: ["small", "medium", "large"],
    prices: [{ small: 150, medium: 220, large: 300 }],
    category: "veg",
    image: "https://www.dominos.co.in/files/items/Margherit.jpg",
    description:
      "A classic margherita pizza with a perfectly prepared base topped with a generous layer of cheese, offering a mouth-watering experience for cheese lovers.",
  },
  {
    name: "Vegie Paradise",
    varients: ["small", "medium", "large"],
    prices: [{ small: 250, medium: 380, large: 500 }],
    category: "veg",
    image:
      "https://www.dominos.co.in/files/items/Digital_Veggie_Paradise_olo_266x265.jpg",
    description:
      "A plain pizza topped with loads of cheese, making it a paradise for cheese lovers.",
  },
];

export default pizzas;
